description:
Adds the character "Wing Diver (EDF5) Civilian Outfit."
Allows you to fight in a "civilian sky dancer" reskin.
Equipment, Abilities, and SP Moves are the same as "Wing Diver (EDF5)," but SP Gauge charges faster.
name: "Additional character" Sky Dancer, Wing Diver (EDF5) Civilian Outfit: Reskin
